ar, 2019|publisher=Sverigetopplistan|accessdate=January 14, 2020}}</ref>\n| 24\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/charts/jahreshitparade/2019|title=Schweizer Jahreshitparade 2019 \u2013 hitparade.ch|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=December 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191229132642/https://hitparade.ch/charts/jahreshitparade/2019|archive-date=December 29, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 70\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-songs-of-2019__28072/|title=The Official Top 40 biggest songs of 2019|publisher=Official Charts Company|last=Copsey|first=Rob|date=January 1, 2020|accessdate=January 1, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101072038/https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-songs-of-2019__28072/|archive-date=January 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 36\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/hot-100-songs|title=Hot 100 Songs \u2013 Year-End 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 6, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206013437/https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/hot-100-songs|archive-date=December 6, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 73\n|-<!-- [[WP:USCHARTS]] applies to all charts, weekly and year-end. Do not add the Alternative Songs chart here. -->\n! scope=\"row\"| US Rock Airplay (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/rock-airplay-songs|title=Rock Airplay Songs \u2013 Year-End 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 6, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205181040/https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/rock-airplay-songs|archive-date=December 5, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 26\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Rolling Stone'' Top 100<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/charts/songs/year-end/|title=Top 100 Songs of 2019|work=[[Rolling Stone]]|date=January 10, 2020|accessdate=January 17, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110235055/https://www.rollingstone.com/charts/songs/year-end/|archive-date=January 10, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 33\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Certifications==\n{{Certification Table Top}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|type=single|award=Platinum|number=2|relyear=2019|certyear=2019|certref=<ref name=\"cert\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=May 27, 2019|accessdate=May 25, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224223551/http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|archive-date=February 24, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Austria|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|accessdate=February 14, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Belgium|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2019|accessdate=November 22, 2019}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Canada|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Platinum|number=3|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2019|accessdate=October 8, 2019|refname=\"cert2\"}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Denmark|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|id=9087|accessdate=April 1, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=France|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Gold|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2020|accessdate=March 17, 2020}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Italy|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Platinum|type=single|relyear=2019|certyear=2019|accessdate=August 5, 2019}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Mexico|artist=Billie Eilish|title=Bury a Friend|award=Platinum|number=3|type=single|relyear=2019|cert