om the daily chart, not the weekly chart. -->56\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ariacharts.com.au/annual-charts/2019/singles-chart|title=ARIA End of Year Singles Chart 2019|publisher=Australian Recording Industry Association|accessdate=January 10, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111005913/https://www.ariacharts.com.au/annual-charts/2019/singles-chart|archive-date=January 11, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 26\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Austria (\u00d63 Austria Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://austriancharts.at/year.asp?cat=s&id=2019|title=Jahreshitparade Singles 2019|website=austriancharts.at|accessdate=January 1, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301200027/https://austriancharts.at/year.asp?cat=s&id=2019|archive-date=March 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 56\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Belgium (Ultratop Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2019|title=Jaaroverzichten 2019|publisher=Ultratop|accessdate=December 20, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200229142909/https://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2019|archive-date=February 29, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 53\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Canada (Canadian Hot 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2019/canadian-hot-100|title=Canadian Hot 100 \u2013 Year-End 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 6, 2019}}</ref>\n| 41\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark (Tracklisten)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitlisten.nu/top2019.asp?list=Track%20100|title=Track Top-100 2019|publisher=Hitlisten|language=Danish|accessdate=January 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114134622/http://www.hitlisten.nu/top2019.asp?list=Track%20100|archive-date=January 14, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| 36\n|-\n! scope=\"row\